al Wagner]] (1938) 2-time MLB All-Star\n* [[Bob Walk]] (1977) MLB All-Star\n* [[Tillie Walker]] (1910\u20131911) 1918 AL Home Run Leader\n* [[Ricky Williams]] (1996\u20131997) NFL Pro-Bowl; 1998 [[Heisman Trophy]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.kcballers.com Official website]\n\n{{Chicago White Sox}}\n{{South Atlantic League}}\n{{North Carolina Sports}}\n\n[[Category:Chicago White Sox minor league affiliates]]\n[[Category:Dale Earnhardt]]\n[[Category:Kannapolis, North Carolina]]\n[[Category:Professional baseball teams in North Carolina]]\n[[Category:Rowan County, North Carolina]]\n[[Category:South Atlantic League teams]]\n[[Category:Baseball teams established in 1995]]\n[[Category:Sports teams in Charlotte, North Carolina]]\n[[Category:1995 establishments in North Carolina]]\n", "name_user": "Ira Leviton", "label": "safe", "comment": "Deleted a duplicate \"the\".", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kannapolis_Cannon_Ballers"}
